Rules for Entities
------------------
Edit: Custom Variables

Edit: Color (or transparent)

Set up: Signals

Loops ( and break loop)

Exit (end event processing)

Comment

------------------

Triggers ("When: ")
-Get signal {listenSignal}
-Entity's variable changed {watchVariable}
-Player steps adjacent
-Player says message (expecting a specific string) {message}
-Player says message (anything)
-Player says message (number)
-Player uses item




Conditions ("If: ")
-Check a variable {variable, ><=?, value}
-Check the player's variables {variable, ><=?, value}
-Player has orbs {numOrbs}
-Player within range {range}



Results
-Say a message {message}
-Send signal {targetEntity}
-Send signal (to all entities)
-Start timer (send signal to self after) {time, signal}
-Move player {position}
-Move entity {position}
-Camera control {changeX, changeY, changeZ}
-Set move route
-Erase entity
-Screen effects
 -Fade in/out
 -Color screen
-Background effects
 -Color areas
 -Color background
-Set Music
-Play Sound Effect



